I am a firm beleiver that druids should have a permanant pet. As Soloers we should have a pet. For one thing we don't get any specialty items to bust our defence nor offence. A pet is a good way to do both. it can takedamage for u and give more attack power. Even though we are good soloers when comeing face to face with anyother class...we get our ass kicked. For example, When i went up against a necro..i was demolished. Between the pet he had and him..I was no match. If I had a pet, it would have been a fair fight.I beleive an taming ability should be implemented. Send email and give replies.
